---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro"
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Usage Guide | Gins-Scripts"
  eyebrow="Guide"
  heading="Quick Setup"
>
  <section class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
    <article class="card">
      <h2 class="m-0 text-[20px] tracking-[-0.02em]">1. URL Pattern</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-ink-soft"><code>/{`{type}`}/{`{software}`}/{`{name}`}</code></p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-ink-soft">Example: <code>/widgets/scriptable/qweather-weather-widget</code></p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2 class="m-0 text-[20px] tracking-[-0.02em]">2. Type / Software Matrix</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-ink-soft"><code>widgets</code>: <code>egern</code>, <code>scripting</code>, <code>scriptable</code></p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-ink-soft"><code>modules</code>: <code>egern</code>, <code>shadowrocket</code>, <code>quantumultx</code>, <code>loon</code>, <code>stash</code>, <code>surge</code></p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-ink-soft"><code>scripts</code>: <code>egern</code>, <code>shadowrocket</code>, <code>quantumultx</code>, <code>loon</code>, <code>stash</code>, <code>surge</code>, <code>scripting</code>, <code>scriptable</code></p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2 class="m-0 text-[20px] tracking-[-0.02em]">3. Scripting Package URLs</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-ink-soft">Directory:</p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-ink-soft"><code>/packages/scripting/qweather-weather-widget/</code></p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-ink-soft"><code>/packages/scripting/datagovsg-dashboard/</code></p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-ink-soft">ZIP:</p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-ink-soft"><code>/packages/scripting/qweather-weather-widget.zip</code></p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-ink-soft"><code>/packages/scripting/datagovsg-dashboard.zip</code></p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2 class="m-0 text-[20px] tracking-[-0.02em]">4. QWeather Keys</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-ink-soft"><code>WEATHER_API_KEY</code>: your key</p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-ink-soft"><code>WEATHER_LOCATION</code>: location id or <code>lng,lat</code></p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-ink-soft"><code>QWEATHER_LANG</code>: <code>zh</code> or <code>en</code></p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-ink-soft"><code>QWEATHER_UNIT</code>: <code>m</code> or <code>i</code></p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-ink-soft"><code>WEATHER_API_HOST</code>: <code>https://devapi.qweather.com</code></p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-ink-soft"><code>WEATHER_NAME</code>: display city name</p>
    </article>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
